exercises.name: Pushups
exercises.description: Raise and lower your body to the ground using your arms.

exercises.name: Sit-ups
exercises.description: Start by lying on your back with your arms across your chest and your knees bent. Using your abdominal muscles, lift your chest toward your knees.

exercises.name: Jumping Jacks
exercises.description: Alternate between jumping with you legs out wide and hands over your head to a resting position with hands at your side and feet together.

exercises.name: High Steps
exercises.description: Walk or run in place, while bringing your knees as high as possible.

exercises.name: Squats
exercises.description: While standing, lower your hips than rise back up using your lower body.

exercises.name: Burpees
exercises.description: Go to the ground, do a pushup, then leap back up.

exercises.name: Plank
exercises.description: Hold your body weight with your forearms like you're doing a pushup that never ends.

exercises.name: Jump rope
exercises.description: Jump over the rope as it passes by your feet.

exercises.name: Curls
exercises.description: With weights in your hands, lift them up from your sides to your chest.

exercises.name: Lunges
exercises.description: Put one leg forward, bent a the knee.

exercises.name: Calf raise
exercises.description: Lift yourself up by pushing off the front of your feet and extending your calves.

exercises.name: Wall Sit
exercises.description: Press your back against the wall and sit at a 90 degree angle(no chair!)

exercises.name: Run in Place
exercises.description: Run in place without moving from your position.

exercises.name: Flutter Kick
exercises.description: Lying on your back, extend your legs above the ground. Alternately move each leg up and down without touching the ground.

exercises.name: Butterfly Stretch
exercises.description: With your legs to your sides, bring the bottom of your feet together. Gently press your knees with your elbows.

exercises.name: Standing Hamstring Stretch
exercises.description: Extend one leg out and bend slightly at the knee with the other leg.

exercises.name: Triceps stretch
exercises.description: Grab your elbow with the opposite hand and pull towards your head.

exercises.name: Pull-Up
exercises.description: Hanging from a bar, pull yourself up so your chin can touch the bar.

exercises.name: Bicycle Kick
exercises.description: Lying on your back, raise your legs up and kick as you were pedaling a bike.

workouts.name: Build up Strength
workouts.description: Want to get stronger. Build up your arm and leg muscles.
